snippet.title: Did The Rock OFFICIALLY Sell Out? Amber Heard back! Beast Wars casting!
snippet.description:
Today on the podcast, I talk about how Amber Heard is trending on twitter following the announcement of AQUAMAN: THE LOST KINGDOM. How Dwyane Johnson might be playing Santa Claus in RED ONE for Amazon...which would double as a massive commercial. Ron Pearlman cast as Optimus Primal in TRANSFORMERS: RISE OF THE BEASTS. And more!
